# Security Fixes Applied - UCM ↔ Odoo Middleware
Date: 2026-03-21

## CRITICAL FIXES (ALL APPLIED ✅)

1. ✅ TLS strict - Changed rejectUnauthorized to true in UcmHttpClient.js
2. ✅ Rate limiting - Added express-rate-limit middleware (100/15min on /api/*)
3. ✅ Input validation - Added express-validator with phone/email validation
4. ✅ CORS - Added cors middleware with whitelist
5. ✅ Sessions HMAC - Now uses crypto.createHmac('sha256') with API_SECRET_KEY
6. ✅ Logs - Removed sensitive data from logs (tokens/challenges)
7. ✅ Webhooks - Added timestamp (30d expiry) and IP whitelist check

## HIGH PRIORITY FIXES (ALL APPLIED ✅)

8. ✅ N+1 queries - Fixed to bulk UPDATE instead of loop
9. ✅ Timer leaks - Verified CallHandler.disconnect() clears setInterval
10. ✅ WebSocket timers - _clearTimers() called before connect()
11. ✅ Connection pooling - HTTP agent with keepAlive:true, maxSockets:50
12. ✅ SQLite indexes - Added idx_calls_contact_phone and idx_calls_status_direction
13. ✅ Cache invalidation - createContact() now invalidates cache
14. ✅ Health thresholds - Memory monitoring (warn >200MB, alert >300MB)
15. ✅ Compression - Added compression middleware (threshold:1024)

## DEPENDENCIES INSTALLED
- express-rate-limit
- compression
- express-validator

All security fixes completed successfully.
